{"tid":1243306,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[維穩] 行會通過公務員加薪　高級加4.75%中低級5.26%","createTime":"2019-06-19T11:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T13:58:02.000Z","uid":116083,"like":7,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7d38ca9bca26e6962b0725799df0099b3c77676f","tid":1243306,"uid":116083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:45:35.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局今日(19日)公布，行政長官會同行政會議已通過2019/20年度公務員薪酬調整方案，高層薪金級別及首長級的公務員加薪4.75%，中級及低級薪金級別的公務員，加薪幅度睇齊為5.26%。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n薪酬調整方案的生效日期追溯至今年4月1日，政府指會盡快將建議提交到立法會財務委員會考慮。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190619/mobile/bkn-20190619180115592-0619_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190619%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190619180115592-0619_00822_001.html&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu%2B8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=64a7397b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190619/mobile/bkn-20190619180115592-0619_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n總薪級表<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/master-pay-scale\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fmaster-pay-scale&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu%2B8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=854678ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/master-pay-scale</a><br />\n<br />\n警務人員薪級表<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/police-pay-scale\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fpolice-pay-scale&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu%2B8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=85c57941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/police-pay-scale</a><br />\n<br />\n一般紀律人員(主任級)薪級表<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/general-disciplined-services-officer-pay-scale\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fgeneral-disciplined-services-officer-pay-scale&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu%2B8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=ac1e9c1f\" data-auto-link tar